HEADWORD: Talismanical
<hw>Tal`is*man"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>talismanique</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or pertaining to a talisman;
having the properties of a talisman, or preservative against evils by
occult influence; magical.</def>⟦br⟧
